{"tid":1687353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留意下有冇酒店申請裝修","createTime":"2019-11-01T18:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T19:01:43.000Z","uid":191733,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd7dbf94d882ffb55b06a4626a2685e2dd54ffa","tid":1687353,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T18:31:15.000Z","msg":"班狗已經問咗灣仔銅鑼灣天后附近嘅酒店，借平台、天台、中間通窿嘅防火層，放便衣上去做高位監視。原來唔只一間酒店應承咗<br />\n<br />\n今個星期六日都會有狗係上面，晏奏12點開始直到夜晚。有望遠鏡嘅麻煩周圍望下，最好影低佢，爆哂D仆街酒店出黎<br />\n<br />\nSource:<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">老豆搵仔</span></strong>"},{"pid":"98810c619cb862ab633e0e801a210063892668e2","tid":1687353,"uid":191733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T18:31:53.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"c88811543b44981f9ce89db01752fc1163e2e19a","tid":1687353,"uid":191733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T18:32:03.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"90b233b1d840e1b7fff6e387bef276aed5e022a0","tid":1687353,"uid":191733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"c74aa4b8d9d3271edb502013372e9f83c4661984","tid":1687353,"uid":191733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T18:33:23.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"3ede2b7b7d5e13f8974a0d5387e1564cf9248ba4","tid":1687353,"uid":191733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T18:33:33.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"d5393d1d5c3459e13f6f3dcefe3cae8ec5d289e6","tid":1687353,"uid":6080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T18:52:56.000Z","msg":"有酒店報警 手足被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609724</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f02de59a69996d0fd86058304ea04f68c7f00011","tid":1687353,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T19:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYzJAWY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%